org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.layouting

Class SamplingFRLayouter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.layouting.FRLayouter
      • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.layouting.SamplingFRLayouter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Operator, UnaryBaseGraphToBaseGraphOperator<LogicalGraph>, UnaryBaseGraphToValueOperator<LogicalGraph,LogicalGraph>, UnaryGraphToGraphOperator, LayoutingAlgorithm

    public class SamplingFRLayouter
extends FRLayouter
    FRLayouter that only considers a random sample of vertices for one side of the repulsion-calculation. Depending on the sampleRate this algorithm is faster then the default one but produces only approximate images.
